{"tid":1220031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】由警方定性暴動及決定開槍 張建宗：港府高層沒參與","createTime":"2019-06-14T02:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T02:22:46.000Z","uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bee57b10a89e9a773ce1d8669da372aa16959c0a","tid":1220031,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:22:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E7%94%B1%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E5%8F%8A%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D-%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E6%B2%92%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87-134300190.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E7%2594%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25A7%258D-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E6%25B2%2592%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587-134300190.html&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=22ac25a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E7%94%B1%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E5%8F%8A%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D-%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E6%B2%92%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87-134300190.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PmbuJ7y9LxIBqyTFGtOw9g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190613a215130.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FPmbuJ7y9LxIBqyTFGtOw9g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190613a215130.jpg&h=277eaa8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張建宗指港府高層沒參與開槍決定。新聞處影片截圖<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】反《逃犯條例》示威演變成激烈衝突，政務司司長張建宗接受Now新聞台訪問時表示，定性為暴動及開槍發射橡膠子彈，是警方按守則及現場情況決定，是當時情況下的最低武力，又指不擔心西方國家對香港經濟採取報復措施。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗多次呼籲年青人表達意見要守法及非暴力，強調政府不會撤回條例。他相信，暴動對香港國際形象只會有片面影響，強調修例已作多重保障亦不擔心外國有報復措施。<br />\n<br />\n至於應否推遲表決或延長審議，張建宗指審議時間這些事情由立法會主席決定，政府會尊重。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁快又割<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}